author: Ubisoft
description:
Tom Clancy's The Division 2 new season, "The Pact", is coming on September 9, Agents!

The Hyenas, Outcast and True Sons seem to be forging a Pact against The Division. One powerful enough to shift the balance of power in DC.

“The Pact” introduces a new set of Modifiers, seasonal events including Halloween and special collaborations, Veteran rewards, and the arrival of a brand-new open-world activity: Retaliation.

About The Division 2:
Tom Clancy's The Division 2 is a shooter RPG with a thrilling campaign fully playable in co-op and multiple PVP modes.

In The Division 2, save your country in Washington, DC, and in the Warlords of New York expansion, hunt down Aaron Keener, a former Agent who has taken control of New York.

#Ubisoft #TheDivision2
